  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large clay or ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, black pepper, and chili flakes. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the mussels, orange juice, and chopped cilantro. Stir to combine.",
    "Cover the tagine and cook for 5-7 minutes, until the mussels are opened.",
    "Discard any mussels that have not opened.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
